item.description:
I have access to FREE stand-up comedy tickets!

Featuring hilarious Boston comics:

Corey Manning - http://www.coreymanni...
Chris Tabb - http://christabb.com/...
The Dynamic Duo - http://www.myspace.co...

The Dynamic Duo of Comedy, the only urban comedy team in the country, is bringing the, funniest, wildest, most unpredictable comedy show you've ever seen to Rhode Island.

This special comedy event will be a DVD taping, come be part of history at Corinnes

There may be other comics added to the roster in the future.

I will be there starting at 6:30 pm for cocktail hour, and the show starts at 7:30 pm.

Please RSVP by 8/29 to reserve your free ticket.
item.name: FREE Stand-Up Comedy @ Corinne's
